00:12:30.050 --> 00:12:30.882
Izvini.

00:12:31.951 --> 00:12:32.850
Izvini.

00:12:35.054 --> 00:12:36.020
- Hoćeš.

00:12:38.057 --> 00:12:39.624
Hoćeš.

00:13:08.120 --> 00:13:11.089
Tvoja poslušnost
nije obavezna.

00:13:44.189 --> 00:13:46.357
Ovo je kraljevstvo.

00:13:46.359 --> 00:13:49.360
I tvoja moć i snaga.

00:13:49.362 --> 00:13:50.695
Sad i zauvek.

00:13:57.202 --> 00:14:00.071
Ne plaši se,
to može da ošteti telo,

00:14:00.073 --> 00:14:02.940
ali ne može da ubije dušu.

00:14:02.942 --> 00:14:05.810
Pre se plaši onoga
što može da ubije

00:14:05.812 --> 00:14:07.745
i telo i dušu,

00:14:08.647 --> 00:14:09.547
u paklu.

00:14:26.698 --> 00:14:27.598
- Zašto?

00:14:28.767 --> 00:14:30.768
Zašto radiš ovo?

00:14:40.846 --> 00:14:42.413
- Imao sam brata.

00:14:43.348 --> 00:14:46.751
Mislim da mi nije bio
posebno drag.

00:14:47.753 --> 00:14:51.656
Jednog dana smo planinarili
iznad okeana,

00:14:51.658 --> 00:14:55.526
i na najvišoj tački
on je stao da napravi pauzu.

00:14:55.528 --> 00:14:57.862
Niko nije bio tamo da to vidi.

00:14:57.864 --> 00:14:58.696
Da vidi mene,

00:14:59.731 --> 00:15:01.799
dok ga guram preko ivice.

00:15:04.069 --> 00:15:06.537
Znaš kakav je to osećaj?

00:15:07.639 --> 00:15:08.539
Ništa.

00:15:10.943 --> 00:15:13.211
Ubio sam svog brata,

00:15:13.213 --> 00:15:14.479
i tako sam se osećao,

00:15:15.414 --> 00:15:16.314
baš tako.

00:15:18.884 --> 00:15:20.785
To me je prestravilo.

00:15:22.554 --> 00:15:24.956
